column1: \nThe new eSmart is a highly efficient and robust machine which has been designed to ensure energy saving up to 75%. With its matt finish Japanese polish design, the 7-star machine is equipped with intelligent technology that allows the user to operate AC from their smartphones. The tropical compressor enables the machine to operate efficiently even at 63°C with stronger air throw

\n

Your Phone is Now Your Air Conditioner Remote

\nAC Freedom is an application that enables a user to remote control Kenwood’s eSmart Air Conditioner from anywhere. The simple interface of AC Freedom app designed for Kenwood eSmart Air Conditioner allows a person to operate all the functions of remote control which are as follow:
\n- Turning on and regulate the temperature,
\n- Check the working condition and set weekly timings of your air conditioner
\n- Designed for Kenwood’s new eSmart air conditioner rather than the whole production line of air conditioners.

column1: \nSafety latch ensure toaster stays closed when in use
\nthere's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM640. From tasty cheese toasties, sandwich melts and panini, experiment with different fillings for your perfect toasted sandwich.

\nThe 700W Kenwood SM640 Sandwich Maker has capacity for two rounds of sandwiches / four slices.
\nIt comes with two sets of removable cooking plates - triangle sandwich plates and grill/griddle plates - designed to toast, grill and griddle a variety of foods.
\nThe plates are non-stick coated so that food can easily be served and for easy cleaning. There are plate release catches and the plates have handles on each side for better handling.
\nA safety latch ensures the sandwich toaster remains closed when in use and rubberized feet ensure it stays in one place.
\nWhen in use as a griddle, it opens flat for ease of cooking.
\nThere are 'on / off' and 'ready' neon indicators to show the power state of the sandwich maker and when it is ready to start cooking.
\nAnd ergonomically-designed carrying handles make the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM640 easy to move and store in the kitchen.

column1: \nKenwood blender is designed to assist with blending ingredients together to make a variety of drinks, soups, dips, etc

\nThe new range of Triblade hand blenders is faster, stronger and even easier to use than ever before. Performance improvements and brand new attachments will help you blend, mash and chop your way to the perfect meal, quickly and effortlessly.

\nOur unique Triblade system is a truly innovative design that combines 3 elements to give you unrivaled performance: angled blades blend more of your food in less time, specially designed ribs reduce suction and the unique foot shape stops splashing, keeping you and your kitchen clean.

\n

Even easier to use and more powerful

\nAn improved motor makes the new range of Triblade 14% more powerful than ever before and able to handle 20% heavier loads – right down to the toughest foods such as frozen fruit and root vegetables.

column1: \nConvenient, quick and easy to use, there's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM650. From tasty cheese toasties, sandwich melts and panini, experiment with different fillings for your perfect toasted sandwich.

\nGrill vegetables and kebabs for healthy nutritious meals. Make sweet snacks and desserts such as waffles, pancakes and fruit turnovers. And for savory snacks and meals try omelets, calzones and crispy burritos.
\nThe 700W Kenwood SM650 Sandwich Maker has capacity for two rounds of sandwiches / four slices.

\nAnd ergonomically-designed carrying handles make the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 650 easy to move and store in the kitchen.

column1: \nConvenient, quick and easy to use, there's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM740. It is our largest and most powerful sandwich maker with a 1300W heating element and capacity for four rounds of sandwiches / eight slices.

\nThere's so much you can do with the white Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 740. It is our largest and most powerful sandwich maker with a 1300W heating element and capacity for four rounds of sandwiches / eight slices.

\nFrom tasty cheese toasties, sandwich melts and panini, experiment with different fillings for your perfect toasted sandwich. Grill vegetables and kebabs for healthy nutritious meals. Make sweet snacks and desserts such as pancakes and fruit turnovers. And for savory snacks and meals try omelets, calzones and crispy burritos.
\nThe Kenwood SM 740 Sandwich Maker comes with two sets of removable cooking plates - triangle sandwich plates and grill/griddle plates - designed to toast, grill and griddle a variety of foods.
\nThe plates are non-stick coated so that food can easily be served and for easy cleaning. There are plate release catches and the plates have handles on each side for better handling.
\nA safety latch ensures the sandwich toaster remains closed when in use and rubberized feet ensure it stays in one place.
\nWhen in use as a griddle, it opens flat for ease of cooking and includes two oil drip trays.
\nThere are 'on / off' and 'ready' neon indicators to show the power state of the sandwich maker and when it is ready to start cooking.
\nAnd ergonomically-designed carrying handles make the Kenwood Sandwich Maker SM 740 easy to move and store in the kitchen.
